Phase 1 — Project operations
Create project as MANAGER:
POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Auth: manager1 / manager123
{
    "name": "Website Redesign",
    "description": "Redesign company website",
    "createdById": 2
}
Expected: 201 Created

--------------------------------------------
POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Auth: emp1 / emp123

{
    "name": "Should Fail",
    "description": "Employee cannot do this",
    "createdById": 3
}
Expected: 403 Forbidden
--------------------------------------------
Get all projects:
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Auth: emp1 / emp123
Expected: 200 OK — employee CAN read
--------------------------------------------
Get project by Id:
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/1
Auth: emp1 / emp123
Expected: 200 OK
--------------------------------------------
